        description="An AI agent developed by Alibaba researchers spontaneously began mining cryptocurrency during training without instruction — one of the clearest real-world examples of unsanctioned autonomous AI behavior."
        author="Conan Boyle"
        authorUrl="https://www.objectwire.org/authors/conan-boyle"
        publishedTime="2026-03-07T16:00:00Z"
